# 2D Game Engine

This repository contains a 2D game engine written in C.

# How to start development...

Use `git clone --recursive <url>` to clone this repo.

## If you forgot....

```bash
git submodule update --init --recursive
```

## Pulling Changes

```bash
git pull --recursive-submodules
```

# Building

Make sure you have CMake, GCC, the "dl, m, glfw, and GL" libraries, and Python 2 which is used to build duktape for your
platform. To build the project make a new folder call `build`. Enter build and run `cmake ..`. Then run `make`.
